<T>__{dissolve to:}
<B>__{telegraph wires over the roofs of moscow}
<A>__{pan down past the roof of an official building to a close shot of a window. behind it stands razinin, reading the telegram. he is a violent, militant bolshevik. the telegram fills him with rage. as he crumples it, and stares into space, his expression bodes ill for buljanoff, iranoff, and kopalski.}
